      "span_text": "The India State-Level Disease Burden Initiative has recently reported the overall trends of diseases, injuries, and risk factors from 1990 to 2016 for every state of India. This analysis was done as part of the Global Burden of Diseases, Injuries, and Risk Factors Study (GBD) 2016, which estimated disease burden of 333 diseases and injuries and 84 risk factors using all accessible data from multiple sources."
